OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,FAccording to Homelessness charity St
OL,7,FMungo's, there are more than 4,500
OL,8,Fpeople sleeping rough in England.
OL,10,FAlmost half of those are in London.
OL,12,FThe charity's Regional Head, Laura
OL,13,FShovlin, said: "SWEP is incredibly
OL,14,Fimportant in terms of saving lives
OL,15,Facross the winter period for people
OL,16,Frough sleeping.
