OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,F"Rough sleeping is dangerous enough as
OL,7,Fit is without it being dangerous or at
OL,8,Fthese temperatures. It is incredibly
OL,9,Fimportant that we respond immediately
OL,10,Fwhen the temperature hits 0.
OL,12,F"Over the SWEP period, we focus on
OL,13,Fstreet outreach. We target the most
OL,14,Fvulnerable, with higher health needs,
OL,15,Fhigher risks around respiratory
OL,16,Fconditions, hypothermia and frostbite,
OL,17,Ffor example.
