OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,F"Extra resources open to try to get
OL,7,Fpeople into accommodation, which is a
OL,8,Fbrilliant opportunity to get people in
OL,9,Fand try to keep them in for good."
OL,11,FThe SWEP alert is guidance given to
OL,12,Fcouncils and charities.
OL,14,FJon Glackin is a coordinator with
OL,15,FStreets Kitchen - a charity that
OL,16,Fprovides hot food to homeless people
OL,17,Fin London. He thinks more needs to be
OL,18,Fdone.
