OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,F"There needs to be a legal obligation,
OL,7,Fwhenever the temperature hits a point
OL,8,Fthat it will kill people on the
OL,9,Fstreet," He said.
OL,11,F"We need a law to come into place that
OL,12,Feverybody has a right to be housed and
OL,13,Faccommodated. We should have that all
OL,14,Fyear round but particularly when it's
OL,15,Fvery cold weather; and very hot
OL,16,Fweather too."
