OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,FSir Sadiq Khan, the Mayor of London,
OL,7,Ffunds a pan-London 'overflow' service,
OL,8,Fwhich will provide additional SWEP
OL,9,Fspaces for homeless people if local
OL,10,Fborough provisions become full.
OL,12,FHe is encouraging people to support
OL,13,Fthe annual winter rough sleeping
OL,14,Fcampaign by contacting support
OL,15,Fservices through the Street Link
OL,16,Fwebsite if they see somebody sleeping
OL,17,Fon the streets.
