OL,3,CHomeless and rough sleepers offered
OL,4,Cshelter as temperatures drop in London
OL,6,FHe said: "I am committed to ending
OL,7,Frough sleeping by 2030 and providing
OL,8,Fsupport to get people off the streets.
OL,9,FHelping people to start rebuilding
OL,10,Ftheir lives is at the centre of our
OL,11,Fplan, as we work together to build a
OL,12,Fsafer, fairer London for everyone."
